{"tid":1993734,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"醫專稱新型肺炎疫情變數及風險仍高 呼籲市民勿鬆懈","createTime":"2020-04-29T03:37:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-29T03:54:39.000Z","uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4ac69c361b9b0245bf7a68666a629f99739be143","tid":1993734,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T03:37:40.000Z","msg":"醫專稱新型肺炎疫情變數及風險仍高 呼籲市民勿鬆懈<br />\n2020-04-29 HKT 11:17<br />\n<br />\n香港醫學專科學院表示，現時新型肺炎疫情帶來的變數和風險仍高，未來兩周是控制社區傳播的關鍵時刻，呼籲市民必須保持警覺，不要鬆懈，盡量留在家中，避免前往人群聚集的地方。<br />\n<br />\n醫專指，經過醫護多月來為抗疫所作出的貢獻，以及市民大眾的共同努力，喜見本港疫情近日有所放緩，提醒市民要繼續保持適當的社交距離，注意個人衛生、戴口罩、勤洗手，保護自己、保護他人，攜手延續「單位數字」以至「零確診」的紀錄。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1523353-20200429.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1523353-20200429.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=C0QxMr2ftqWfBh1dRblImP3PLjr3aI%2Bxco%2FW%2FCjCBac%3D&h=b0f73746\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1523353-20200429.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=fcfcd121\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1523353-20200429.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">又未來關鍵兩周，呵欠</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e574d8f85d8bfedcfcadb73c8a7b293515bcf6c8","tid":1993734,"uid":235015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T03:51:03.000Z","msg":"咁叫林鄭咪撚放班支那學生落黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bb9d8e31b1096f6a9e70457730f97d334bd6cf6","tid":1993734,"uid":212702,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T03:52:32.000Z","msg":"大家請合作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n人生中有欢喜<br />\n难免亦常有泪<br />\n我哋大家&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"a65c7b87f76e